/** * Whether to log form data at DEBUG level, and headers at TRACE level. * Both may contain sensitive information. *

By default set to {@code false} so that request details are not shown. * @param enable whether to enable or not */ public void setEnableLoggingRequestDetails(boolean enable) { this.enableLoggingRequestDetails = enable. }

code: /**  * Whether any logging of values being encoded or decoded is explicitly  * disabled regardless of log level.  */ public boolean isEnableLoggingRequestDetails() {     return this.enableLoggingRequestDetails. }
